Ing '''West Virginia''' ({{Audio-IPA|en-us-West Virginia.ogg|/ˌwɛstvɚˈdʒɪnjə/}}) metung yang [[U.S. state|state]] king [[Appalachia]]n, [[Upland South]], ampong [[Mid-Atlantic States|Mid-Atlantic]] labuad na ning [[United States]], kasepu ne ing [[Virginia]] keng maulingaslagan, [[Kentucky]] keng maulingalbugan, [[Ohio]] keng pangulungalbugan, ampong [[Pennsylvania]] ampong [[Maryland]] pangulungaslagan. Ing kayang tungku (kabisera) ampong pekamaragul diling lakanablen iyapin ing [[Charleston, West Virginia|Charleston]].


